Objective

The objective of this task was to:

Create a secure and efficient relational database
Store candidate and interview information properly
Maintain monitoring logs during interviews
Save AI-generated risk scores and evaluations
Support future scalability and analytics
Scope of Work

The work focused on:

Database schema design
Relational table creation
Primary and foreign key implementation
SQL query development
Data modeling and relationships
Database normalization
Testing table relationships and constraints
