9. Challenges & Solutions
Challenge	Solution
Foreign key datatype mismatch	Used consistent INT datatype
Table relationship errors	Added proper foreign key constraints
Redundant data risk	Applied normalization concepts
Query testing issues	Performed validation and debugging


